text: Asim Azhar (Urdu: عاصم اظہر; conceived 29 October 1996) is a Pakistani vocalist, lyricist, performer and an entertainer. He began his profession as a vocalist on YouTube, covering contemporary Western melodies before he turned into a person of note. == References == == Other websites == * Asim Azhar at IMDb * Asim Azhar at Instagram Category:Living people Category:1996 births Category:Pakistani singer-songwriters
